  "prompt": "What are some popular drink/shots to get at the bar?",
  "response": "Certainly! Here is a list of popular drinks and shots often ordered at bars:\n\n### Classic Cocktails:\n1. **Margarita** - Tequila, lime juice, and triple sec with a salted rim.\n2. **Martini** - Gin or vodka, dry vermouth, usually garnished with an olive or a lemon twist.\n3. **Old Fashioned** - Whiskey, sugar, Angostura bitters, and a twist of citrus rind.\n4. **Mojito** - White rum, sugar, lime juice, soda water, and mint.\n5. **Cosmopolitan** - Vodka, triple sec, cranberry juice, and lime juice.\n6. **Mai Tai** - Light rum, dark rum, lime juice, orange cura\u00e7ao, and orgeat syrup.\n7. **Negroni** - Gin, Campari, and sweet vermouth.\n8. **Whiskey Sour** - Whiskey, lemon juice, sugar, and optionally an egg white.\n9. **Pi\u00f1a Colada** - Rum, coconut cream, and pineapple juice.\n10. **Gin and Tonic** - Gin and tonic water, with lime.\n\n### Popular Shots:\n1. **Tequila Shot** - Typically served with a wedge of lime and salt.\n2. **J\u00e4gerbomb** - A shot of J\u00e4germeister dropped into a glass of Red Bull.\n3. **Kamikaze** - Vodka, triple sec, and lime juice.\n4. **Lemon Drop** - Vodka, lemon juice, and sugar.\n5. **B-52** - Layered shot of Kahl\u00faa, Baileys, and Grand Marnier.\n6. **Irish Car Bomb** - A shot of Irish cream and Irish whiskey dropped into a pint of stout.\n7. **Washington Apple** - Canadian whiskey, sour apple schnapps, and cranberry juice.\n8. **Mind Eraser** - Vodka, Kahl\u00faa, and soda water.\n9. **Woo Woo** - Vodka, peach schnapps, and cranberry juice.\n10. **Gold Rush** - Goldschl\u00e4ger cinnamon schnapps.\n\nThese are just a few examples, and drink preferences can vary based on region, season, and personal taste. Enjoy responsibly!",
